params.markdown:
## Azure AI Foundry

Key performance and usage metrics monitored for Azure AI Foundry. This dashboard includes:

- Request rates
- Latency
- Error rates
- Token usage

embeddableConfig.description: Request count over the time by LLM models.
embeddableConfig.title: Request rate - by model

embeddableConfig.description: Availability percentage with the following calculation: (Total Calls - Server Errors)/Total Calls. Server Errors include any HTTP responses >=500
embeddableConfig.title: Overall model availability

embeddableConfig.description: Average model usage latency grouped by LLM models.
embeddableConfig.title: Latency - by model

embeddableConfig.description: For streaming requests; Model token generation rate, measured in milliseconds.
embeddableConfig.title: Time between tokens - by model

embeddableConfig.description: Average time it takes for first byte of response data to be received after request is made by model,
embeddableConfig.title: Time to first byte - by model

embeddableConfig.description: For streaming and non-streaming requests; time it takes for last byte of response data to be received after request is made by model.
embeddableConfig.title: Time to last byte - by model

embeddableConfig.description: Total token usage by LLM model
embeddableConfig.title: Token usage - by model

embeddableConfig.description: Total error count over time by LLM model.
embeddableConfig.title: Error rate - by model
